This software is designed for educational purposes only. The vulnerable 
applications contained within this project are intentionally insecure and 
should NEVER be deployed in a production environment or accessible from the 
internet.

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any misuse of this 
software or any damages that may result from its use. Users are expected to 
use this software responsibly and only for legitimate educational and 
training purposes.

By using this software, you agree to:
1. Use it only for educational purposes
2. Not deploy vulnerable applications in production
3. Not use the techniques learned for malicious purposes  
4. Follow responsible disclosure practices
5. Respect applicable laws and regulations

This project is intended to help security professionals, developers, and 
students understand XSS vulnerabilities and learn proper prevention techniques.